data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Minutes to I-79 & downtown Houston. Houston Park & all of its amenities are just steps away! Relax on the inviting covered front porch or on the newer 3-tiered rear deck while taking in a game at the park. A fully fenced-in, level back yard also includes a storage shed and additional off-street parking. A brand NEW roof is scheduled to be installed in early December. Inside, you will find plenty of charming character, nice-sized rooms, and an open layout. Rounded archways, original wood details, & a gas insert fireplace add to the coziness of the first floor. The roomy kitchen also provides access to the rear deck. Upstairs you will find 3 nice-sized bedrooms and a newly remodeled full bath featuring new fixtures, vanity, & a gorgeous tile floor. The dry basement provides a 2nd full bath, A TON of extra storage, & access to the back yard. Attic space provides more storage. Stop by to see all that this charmer has to offer! 1-year home warranty is included!
